<br>
Anyway I first learned of this quest a level 20 ... decided to try it at 22 and sure enough, was able to complete it that early. The person who told me about the quest said she had done it at level 12 with help... I don't doubt it for a minute. The Staff of Wheel is awsome for such lower levels although I did miss out on alot of offense skill points due to the long swing time of the staff.<br>
<br>
